{"id":232387433,"title":"內有選手求推薦！","content":"最近想買書了，發現從國中後就好久沒有好好坐著細細品嚐一本書，找了一些選手！拜託各位推薦了🙏\nhttps://i.imgur.com/B6uzi6q.jpg\n這本的序讓我雞皮疙瘩，但他是一篇一篇的，就以前讀的來說我都是看整本一個故事的，有看過一篇一篇的，但是他給我的感覺就好像要畫一幅日落然後整個倒影畫的很美但發現沒有橘色黃色顏料了，有種沒辦法入戲很深，沒辦法走到深處，一下就沒了的感覺：（\nhttps://i.imgur.com/FkkD6nE.jpg\n這本猶豫的點如上，但，這本真的，好燒啊！！\nhttps://i.imgur.com/uc7uDfp.jpg\n我對漱石的印象還停留在月亮真美，想體會把墨水當飲料喝的人生經驗，但不確定自己有把握讀完😂😂\n\n以上這些，請大大推薦一本了！🙇🏻‍♂️🙇🏻‍♂️","excerpt":"最近想買書了，發現從國中後就好久沒有好好坐著細細品嚐一本書，找了一些選手！拜託各位推薦了，這本的序讓我雞皮疙瘩，但他是一篇一篇的，就以前讀的來說我都是看整本一個故事的，有看過一篇一篇的，但是他給我的感","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"e0a290f4-752b-48a2-a791-f211f8b46588","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-10-28T03:04:16.990Z","updatedAt":"2019-10-28T03:04:16.990Z","commentCount":5,"likeCount":7,"tags":[],"topics":["推薦書單","書籍","小說","言情小說"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"書籍","forumAlias":"book","school":"朝陽科技大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":7}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/B6uzi6q.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/FkkD6nE.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/uc7uDfp.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"abeee747-50c5-47a2-83fa-f7940dab50a3","url":"https://i.imgur.com/B6uzi6ql.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/B6uzi6ql.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/B6uzi6ql.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED_FAILED"],"createdAt":"2019-10-28T03:04:16.990Z","updatedAt":"2019-10-28T03:04:16.990Z"},{"id":"abeee747-50c5-47a2-83fa-f7940dab50a3","url":"https://i.imgur.com/B6uzi6q.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/B6uzi6q","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/B6uzi6ql.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED_FAILED"],"createdAt":"2019-10-28T03:04:16.990Z","updatedAt":"2019-10-28T0